2	/**
3	 * hook-gym.ts — Synthetic problem runner with hook observability.
4	 *
5	 * Spawns cheap agents (haiku/sonnet) on simple synthetic problems
6	 * with --include-hook-events to capture full hook lifecycle.
7	 *
8	 * Usage:
9	 *   npx tsx scripts/hook-gym.ts --list
10	 *   npx tsx scripts/hook-gym.ts --run probe-hooks --dry-run
11	 *   npx tsx scripts/hook-gym.ts --run probe-hooks
12	 *   npx tsx scripts/hook-gym.ts --run-all
13	 *   npx tsx scripts/hook-gym.ts --replay <log-file>
14	 *
15	 * See docs/hook-gym-spec.md for full design.
